
Our official Dutch 'Stichting Peer to Peer Alternatives', which has a European Union pic number, has participated in three official research consortia. See also the projects of the P2P Lab until 2019, and the activities of the Belgian nonprofit being created in 2020.

The coordinator of the P2P Foundation Research network is [[Jose Ramos]].


